==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Classman
<hw>Class"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Classmen</plw><pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A member of a
class; a classmate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A candidate for graduation in arts who is placed in
an honor class, as opposed to a passman, who is not classified.</def>
<mark>[Oxford, Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Classmate</ent>⟦br⟧
